#############################################################
## Building and installing CGAL                            ##
#############################################################

Running:

 sudo apt-get install libcgal-dev

will install v. 4.0.*
Instead download newest (4.3) from CGAL webpage, and run

 sudo tar xzf CGAL.4.3.tar.gz
 cd CGAL.4.3/
 sudo cmake .
 sudo make
 sudo make install

Before running cmake, one may have to install some boost-packages:

 # To install alot:
 sudo apt-get install libboost1.49

 # I only needed
 sudo apt-get install libboost-system1.49

Furthermore, ldconfig was needed:

 sudo ldconfig